android.permission.SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM.description: Allows an app to use exact alarm scheduling APIs to perform timing sensitive background work.

android.permission.USE_EXACT_ALARM.info: allows using exact alarms without user permission.
android.permission.USE_EXACT_ALARM.description: Allows apps to use exact alarms just like with SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM but without needing to request this permission from the user. This is only intended for use by apps that rely on exact alarms for their core functionality. You should continue using SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM if your app needs exact alarms for a secondary feature that users may or may not use within your app.  Keep in mind that this is a powerful permission and app stores may enforce policies to audit and review the use of this permission. Such audits may involve removal from the app store if the app is found to be misusing this permission.

playstore_details.title: Alpha Progression Gym Tracker
playstore_details.description:
Gym Workout Planner & Tracker - Alpha Progression.
Maximize your gains and track your gym workout routines & programs with Alpha Progression - the ultimate fitness app. Our app goes beyond creating a personalized workout plan; it empowers you to track your progress and achieve your fitness goals. With an extensive exercises database and expert recommendations, we provide the guidance you need to embark on an effective workout routine & muscle building journey.

PERSONALIZED MUSCLE BUILDING & WEIGHT LIFTING WORKOUT PROGRAMS
Experience gym workout plans backed by science, tailored to your objectives and needs. With Alpha Progression, you can choose your training frequency and target muscles during your gym workouts.

GYM WORKOUT TRACKER - TRACK YOUR WORKOUT ROUTINES
Our gym tracker feature includes a rep counter, weight lifting and RIR tracker, allowing you to monitor your progress. Our note-taking and gym log features help enhance your strength training. Plus, our convenient rest timer keeps you in sync with your next set.

GYM WORKOUT PLANNER - REACH YOUR WEIGHT LIFTING GOALS
We celebrate your achievements by providing a list of personal records and milestones. That way, we ensure you're constantly inspired and rewarded for your hard work. For both men or women, our app creates personalized strength training plans to elevate your gym workout routine & muscle building journey. You can create your own plans for added customization.

PROGRESSION RECOMMENDATIONS
Get the most out of your gym workout routine with our advanced algorithm. By analyzing your past workout programs & performances, we provide you with recommendations on weight lifting and reps, ensuring you achieve maximum muscle gain through progressive overload.

VAST EXERCISE DATABASE - 690 VIDEOS
With our extensive library of 690 exercise videos, you'll learn and perform each exercise with precision and safety. With our exercise evaluations you'll gain insights into the muscle building & strength training potential of each exercise. Categorized by targeted muscles and equipment, you’ll always find ideal gym workout programs.

GET INSIGHTS
Optimize your strength training with our graphs and insights. Visualize your workout programs history,  and analyze how your muscle building and strength training have evolved over time thanks to the gym tracker.

COMPREHENSIVE PERIODIZATION
You can structure your weight training & strength workouts in cycles and deloads. Also create a progressive plan where the number of sets and the level of effort (RIR) increase gradually week by week. This approach ensures progressive overload and promotes continuous gains, helping you maximize your results and achieve your fitness objectives.

SHARE YOUR PLANS
Share your gym workout planner, routines & programs with friends or coaching clients. Easily distribute your plans, allowing recipients to customize them according to their needs.

DATA EXPORT
Export your training data as a .csv file, compatible with apps like Excel. This feature enables you to analyze your statistics, easily tracking your progress

SUBSCRIPTIONS
Enjoy the free version of Alpha Progression, or unlock the full potential with our Pro version. Subscribing to Pro grants you access to exclusive features such as the plan generator, progression recommendations, graphical analytics, and more.

Do you have questions about the app? Please send us an email at info@alphaprogression.com

Terms of service: https://alphaprogression.com/terms
Privacy policy: https://alphaprogression.com/privacy

warning.description:
Permission: android.permission.INSTALL_PACKAGES [android:exported=true]
A Broadcast Receiver is found to be shared with other apps on the device therefore leaving it accessible to any other application on the device. It is protected by a permission which is not defined in the analysed application. As a result, the protection level of the permission should be checked where it is defined. If it is set to normal or dangerous, a malicious application can request and obtain the permission and interact with the component. If it is set to signature, only applications signed with the same certificate can obtain the permission.
